---
title: "checkUpkeep (Payment Abstraction V2)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_paused: checkUpkeep() called
    q_check_paused --> q_check_role: contract not paused
    q_check_paused --> q_return_false: contract paused
    q_check_role --> q_check_asset_out: caller has AUCTION_WORKER_ROLE
    q_check_role --> q_return_false: unauthorized
    q_check_asset_out --> q_iter_assets: assetOut is configured
    q_check_asset_out --> q_return_false: assetOut not configured
    q_iter_assets --> q_check_asset_config: for asset in s_allowlistedAssets
    q_check_asset_config --> q_check_asset_price: asset is configured (soft skip)
    q_check_asset_config --> q_iter_next: asset not configured (skip)
    q_check_asset_price --> q_check_out_price: assetPrice valid and not stale
    q_check_asset_price --> q_iter_next: asset price invalid (skip)
    q_check_out_price --> q_check_live: assetOutPrice valid (zeros eligible list if invalid)
    q_check_out_price --> q_check_end: assetOutPrice invalid
    q_check_live --> q_check_start_size: no live auction for asset
    q_check_live --> q_check_end: live auction exists
    q_check_start_size --> q_add_start: totalUsdValue >= minAuctionSizeUsd
    q_check_start_size --> q_iter_next: below minimum (skip)
    q_add_start --> q_iter_next: add asset to startEligible list
    q_check_end --> q_check_elapsed: auction exists for asset
    q_check_elapsed --> q_add_end: auctionStart + auctionDuration < block.timestamp
    q_check_elapsed --> q_check_dust: auction not elapsed
    q_check_dust --> q_add_end: remainingUsdValue < minAuctionSizeUsd
    q_check_dust --> q_iter_next: still above minimum
    q_add_end --> q_iter_next: add asset to endEligible list
    q_iter_next --> q_iter_assets: more assets
    q_iter_next --> q_build_result: no more assets
    q_build_result --> q_return_true: startEligible or endEligible not empty
    q_build_result --> q_return_false: both lists empty
    q_return_true --> [*]: return (true, performData)
    q_return_false --> [*]: return (false, empty)

    note right of q_check_start_size
        INV-001: totalUsdValue includes balance in both FeeAggregator and auction contract
        INV-002: Soft checks skip ineligible assets without reverting
        INV-003: An asset can appear in endEligible if elapsed OR if remaining balance below min size (dust guard)
    end note
